<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>关于我 - 我的个人博客</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="brand-mark gradient-button" aria-label="Poppis">
        <span class="gradient-text">Poppis</span>
      </a>
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="brand-block">
          <p class="brand-kicker">About</p>
          <h1 class="logo"><a href="/">我的博客</a></h1>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="/">首页</a>
          <a href="/about" class="active">关于我</a>
          <% if (user) { %>
            <a href="/poppis-console/dashboard">后台管理</a>
          <% } %>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="main">
    <div class="container prose-shell">
      <section class="page-hero">
        <p class="section-kicker">Profile</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">关于我</h1>
        <p class="page-summary">这里不是标准简历，更像一页持续更新的作者侧写，记录我关心的问题、写作方向和做事方式。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-highlights">
        <div class="about-highlight-card">
          <span class="manifesto-index">写</span>
          <div>
            <h3>长期写作</h3>
            <p>记录那些值得沉淀、能反复回看的主题。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-highlight-card">
          <span class="manifesto-index">做</span>
          <div>
            <h3>持续实践</h3>
            <p>把想法和项目都落到真实页面、真实内容里。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-highlight-card">
          <span class="manifesto-index">想</span>
          <div>
            <h3>保留判断</h3>
            <p>不追求信息堆积，更重视清晰表达与长期价值。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <article class="about-page">
        <div class="about-content">
          <%- about.content %>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="footer-kicker">About the author</p>
        <h3>欢迎通过文章先认识我。</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/">首页</a>
        <% if (user) { %>
          <a href="/poppis-console/dashboard">工作台</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 我的个人博客.</p>
      <p class="footer-copy footer-beian">
        <a href="https://beian.mps.gov.cn/#/query/webSearch?code=61030402000136" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="beian-link">
          <img src="/images/beian-badge.svg" alt="公安备案图标" class="beian-icon">
          <span>陕公网安备61030402000136号</span>
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
